snippet.title: Amber Heard Walks Away With 7 Million Dollars
snippet.description:
In a relationship that only lasted one year Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have officially divorce and made a settlement where Amber Heard receives 7 million dollars. She plans to use that money for charity. All allegations and restraining orders have been lifted as the two try to remain friends.
